Examples

Parametric Analysis Integration

Using GUI settings as objectives

Use the output settings in Femtet as simple objective functions.

Single Objective Optimization

Inductance of a Solenoid Coil

In magnetic field analysis, set the self-inductance of a finite-length solenoid coil to a specific value.

Resonant Frequency of Circular Patch Antenna

In electromagnetic wave analysis, set the resonant frequency of a circular patch antenna to a specific value.

Multi-Objective Optimization

Heating Element on Substrate

In thermal conduction analysis, minimize the temperature of the IC chip on the substrate and the size of the substrate.

Air cooling of IC Substrate

In simple fluid-thermal analysis, minimize the temperature of the IC chip on the substrate and the size of the substrate under forced convection.

Parallel Computing

Heating Element on Substrate (Parallel Computing)

Speed up ‘Heating Element on Substrate’ using parallel computing in multiple Femtet instances.

CAD Integration

External CAD (NX) Integration

Explore dimensions of sturdy and lightweight H-beams using NX integration.

External CAD (Solidworks) Integration

Explore the same problem as left with Solidworks integration.

Constrained Model

Strict constraint

Constrains combinations of variables.
